-- Paladino Apologizes for Comments About Gay, Lesbian Community
-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 2010-10-12T21:48:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-12/paladino-apologizes-for-comments-about-gay-lesbian-community.html
Carl Paladino, a candidate for New
York governor, said he apologized for any comments he made that
may have offended the gay and lesbian community, in an e-mailed
statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
